title: Apocrypha Bibliorum Hebraicorum (ABH)
$comment: The Online Key To Apocryphal Texts collects and freely distributes information about ancient texts related to, or inspired by, the Hebrew Bible. The numbering system follows Haelwyck, Clavis apocryphorum Veteris Testamenti (Brill, 1998).
